SubjectRegulations Amending the Canada Production Insurance Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADA PRODUCTION INSURANCE REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to make non-substantive housekeeping amendments to the Regulations that would: (1) address a redundant definition; (2) correct inconsistent use of terms; (3) correct grammatical errors; and, (4) add further clarification.
